    \ \nIt actively integrates diverse information sources, checks for internal consistency and coherence, \nresolves contradictions\
    \ (e.g., using \U0001F72EHEGELIAN_KERNEL or belief revision mechanisms), and strives \nto build a robust, predictive,\
